              "message" : "\nPL/SQL procedure successfully completed.\n\n\n---------------------------\n\nPL/SQL procedure successfully completed.\n\n\n---------------------------\n\nPROFILE_ID    PROFILE_NAME              STATUS     DESCRIPTION    CREATED                                LAST_MODIFIED                          ORACLE_MAINTAINED    \n          193 OCI_CRED$PROF             ENABLED                   14-APR-25 06.29.19.505837000 PM UTC    14-APR-25 06.29.19.505837000 PM UTC    N                    \n          231 RAG_PROFILE               ENABLED                   12-JUN-25 08.31.36.664948000 PM UTC    12-JUN-25 08.31.36.664948000 PM UTC    N                    \n          226 ENCODE_CREDENTIAL$PROF    ENABLED                   22-MAY-25 09.34.30.600760000 PM UTC    22-MAY-25 09.34.30.600760000 PM UTC    N                    \n\n\n---------------------------\n",
